Usage: deleteBNet [-help] [-moduleBased <moduleName>] {-bus <busName> | -busFromBit <busBitName>}

-help                        # Prints out the command usage
-bus <busName>               # Delete top level bus net by given bus net name
                             # (string, optional)
-busFromBit <busBitName>     # Delete sub module bus net by given a bus bit net
                             # name (string, optional)
-moduleBased <moduleName>    # Delete net in the module, using -bus or
                             # -busFromBit for net name (string, optional)